aa(lp58
VNow honeybees tend to be the charismatic representative
p59
aVfor the other 19,900-plus species
p60
aVbecause there's something about honeybees
p61
aVthat draws people into their world.
p62
aVHumans have been drawn to honeybees
p63
aVsince early recorded history,
p64
aVmostly to harvest their honey,
p65
aVwhich is an amazing natural sweetener.
