aa(lp82
VHoneybees can be considered a super-organism,
p83
aVwhere the colony is the organism
p84
aVand it's comprised of 40,000 to 50,000
p85
aVindividual bee organisms.
p86
aVNow this society has no central authority.
p87
aVNobody's in charge.
p88
aVSo how they come to collective decisions,
p89
aVand how they allocate their tasks and divide their labor,
p90
aVhow they communicate where the flowers are,
p91
aVall of their collective social behaviors are mindblowing.
