aa(lp253
VAnd it's not just our honeybees.
p254
aVAll of our beautiful wild species of bees
p255
aVare at risk, including those tomato-pollinating bumblebees.
p256
aVThese bees are providing backup for our honeybees.
p257
aVThey're providing the pollination insurance
p258
aValongside our honeybees.
p259
aVWe need all of our bees.
